Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------TEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要逃学…去远方的什么地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为被看见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没什么好放在心上的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人都没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.89,0:02:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都因为悠你准备时故意磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是故意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知不知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班长她眼睛通红诶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么想肯定都有些内情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日野君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请放心吧  那件事我不会告诉任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…我觉得那样做很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为一个人  这么做太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直喜欢春日野君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直以为你是个温柔  认真又出色的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不会和你说话了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我隐隐约约有些猜到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我希望是自己猜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们…一直以来都是分开的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阔别许久回到我身边的穹  已经不是我所认识的妹妹了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成了我从没见过的  一个纤弱柔美的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我真的…心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生过许多事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每每都会让我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然那家伙很不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也因此  被她所依靠的时候更加让我怦然心动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就想去守护她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她是我妹妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她是我妹妹…不能跨出那一步…我总是这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是在两年后的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有了一段别的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我想把它变成一段真正的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但总是不太顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我却依然想把它硬撑下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果伤害了奈绪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是不太顺利呢  真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为一个人  这么做太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我希望是自己猜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭做好咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠？你怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实一点都没有改变呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你怎么糟蹋我的身体都没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要悠你想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:07:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的…不是这样的  不是这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是结束吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是接吻…还是更亲昵的举动…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是兄妹啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在说这些？为什么是兄妹就不能接吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不许性爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可那个…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为不会被别人接受？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事情我一点都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.93,0:08:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要和悠在一起就好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道还有其它很多问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但全部都无所谓！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管发生什么  就算是悠的小孩我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现实没你想得那么简单！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那万一有了就堕掉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说得那么轻松…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要说那些话？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经讨厌我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔发来短信了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:51.07,pos2,NTP,0,0,0,,（我和真里子都在考虑让你们能\N过上安心的生活。只要你们方便\N的话，两个人分别住到我和真里\N子这边来怎么样。我和真里子一\N直都承蒙大哥照顾，所以我想我\N们也有将你们抚养成人的义务。\N具体等我回国之后直接见面谈吧。\N你和穹两个人都好好考虑一下。）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔他们要回日本了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像和旭川阿姨已经谈过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经被发觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们其实没多少储蓄…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢  这又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:10:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他们一个人可以收养我们中的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么  难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们分开吧  这样才会更幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹  穹你在睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我进来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:45.43,pos2,NTP,0,0,0,,（我虽然是悠的妹妹\N却想和悠接吻…\N想和悠连结在一起…\N但是这好像给悠添麻烦了呢…\N对不起…）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:11:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹她…她不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少可以确定  她应该没有乘电车
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想她可能去别人家了  但哪里都没有人影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他还有哪些有可能的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的活动范围应该不会很大…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:12:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在音乐教室里我没和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穹她和我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.69,0:13:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「这样就扯平了」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个夏天  小穹她好像看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穹她是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你还想和她分开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说正因为如此  你才要和她分开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在寻找答案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再去亮平家什么的看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  谢谢你  奈绪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去我家后面的湖从头开始吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:14:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,位于我们叉依姬神社内社的湖泊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说是万物起源
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比淤能碁吕岛更早存在  乃人类诞生之地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要去那儿的话人就可以转世重生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人生就能从头开始了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该怎么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样  穹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  穹  没能救你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  也许这是最好的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让两人一同前往只有两个人的遥远世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为再也不会睁开眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹  已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很害怕  对于两人的前途
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟会有什么等待着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我依然不知道该如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  两个人一起寻找好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找能好好珍惜这份心意的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不计较他人怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不在意自己会多痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想找到最能让穹得到幸福的路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暖和吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  很暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.10,0:18:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你  穹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久违
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得这些成员凑在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉挺怀念的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也感觉是他们把我们凑到了一块
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有发短信过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那次之后音讯全无
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.23,0:19:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们刚离开机场准备坐巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再换乘几次当地的长途汽车和地区短线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.49,0:19:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概三天后到达目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到受过父母照顾的一个家具商的镇上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是天方夜谭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤身两人去外国居住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不懂  这样真的能幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  对小悠来说  真正的挑战还在后头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.44,0:20:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就我而言  却不能断言小悠是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为  爱上一个人的感情是无法抑止的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我希望他们能得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光有感情就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不能这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有感情就能为所欲为的话  我也有很多想做的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沾到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎饼干  在嘴边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擦掉没
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擦掉了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------M---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从伊福部小姐那里知道了来龙去脉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.38,0:23:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也问过家里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.02,0:23:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我必须得来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:23.72,title3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(313,305)}初佳与悠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.80,0:23:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初佳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.77,0:23:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我比你小又不可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.40,0:23:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没工作也挣不了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.25,0:23:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业后我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.13,0:23:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请永远留在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.11,0:23:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.35,0:23:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于明白了来这里的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.05,0:23:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了  我停止的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.34,0:23:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.26,0:23:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.07,0:24:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.43,0:24:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.48,0:24:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初佳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.14,0:24:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出洋相了
